A plugin for xsbt creating zipfiles with unix exeutable bits

To build this code, get and install SBT from 
    https://github.com/harrah/xsbt

Build and publish the plugin:
    git clone git@github.com:ritschwumm/xsbt-zipper.git
    cd xsbt-zipper
    sbt publish-local
    
Add the plugin to your project in project/plugins.sbt:
    addSbtPlugin("de.djini" % "xsbt-zipper" % "0.1.1")
    
Include the plugin in you project's build.sbt:

    zipperSettings

    zipperFiles	:= Seq(
    	file	-> name
    )

Run the zipper task to get a zipfile.
